<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title><%= title %> - Projects</title>
  <style>
    /* Styling for the body */
    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    
    /* Styling for the main content section */
    main {
      flex: 1;
    }
    
    /* Styling for the footer */
    footer {
      background-color: #333;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    /* Styling for project images */
    .project img {
      max-width: 50%;
      height: auto;
    }
  </style>
  <!-- Link to the main CSS file -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
background-repeat: no-repeat;
background-size: cover; background-image: url('profile.jpg');">
  <!-- Include the header file -->
  <%- include('header') %>
  
  <main>
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <div class="project-container">
      <div class="project">
        <img src="images/project1.jpg" alt="Project 1">
        <h3>Project 1</h3>
        <p>
          <li>Designed a responsive, user-oriented website for shop owners for the on-going process in renting a shop.</li>
          <li>The main objective of the proposed system is to automate the rent paid for the shops by the renter.</li>
          <li>The software used is Visual Basic 6.0 as front end and back end along with MS Access as database.</li>
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="project">
        <img src="images/project2.jpg" alt="Project 2">
        <h3>Project 2</h3>
        <p>
          <li>Developed a web app for booking adventure camps by choosing areas or countries.</li>
          <li>The system has the option to search for and reserve the seat.</li>
          <li>The front end uses HTML, back end uses ASP.NET and MS SQL as database.</li>
        </p>
      </div>
  
      <div class="project">
        <img src="images/project3.jpg" alt="Project 3">
        <h3>Project 3</h3>
        <p>
          <li>Develop a system used for a pharmacy that helps automate the pharmacy workflow.</li>
          <li>Creates a database for managing medicines, customers, orders, and employees.</li>
          <li>Database created using Oracle DBMS.</li>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2023 My Portfolio.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
